Domestic and family violence helplines

To find support services in your area, visit our find local support page. In an emergency call the police on Triple Zero (000).

DVConnect Womensline
1800 811 811

Womensline helps women to obtain safe refuge accommodation, confidential counselling and referral to other services. (24 hours, 7 days a week)
